README 

integrating MPU6050
08/17/2017
davidjun

connect the CJMCU-861 breakout module to the Pi:
 - Vcc to 5V
 - Gnd to Gnd
 - SDA to SDA (pin 3)
 - SCL to SCL (pin 5)
 - AD0 to Gnd

add pull ups if required (not required for the CJMCU-861)

scan i2c bus for device (1 for rev 2 Pis, 0 for rev 1 Pi)
should see 0x68 because we set AD0 to gnd
>> sudo i2cdetect -y 1

ping the IMU with a WHO AM I
should return 0x68
>> sudo i2cget -y 1 0x68 0x75

install Python support
>> sudo apt-get install python-smbus
>> sudo pip3 install mpu6050-raspberrypi

run test script
>> python3 test_mpu6050.py

